1274
01:30:30,805 --> 01:30:33,536
and, I'm sorry to say, we need
the same excellent helper

1275
01:30:33,537 --> 01:30:35,569
who's currently helping you.

1276
01:30:35,570 --> 01:30:37,036
Him.

1277
01:30:37,037 --> 01:30:38,368
That's right, Ngoc Lan.

1278
01:30:38,371 --> 01:30:40,970
I have to go with
these guys to Norway.

1279
01:30:43,302 --> 01:30:46,002
So you say

1280
01:30:46,003 --> 01:30:48,902
Paul go with you Norway?

1281
01:30:48,904 --> 01:30:50,902
That's the situation.

1282
01:30:50,904 --> 01:30:54,703
- Emergency situation!
- And deeply humanitarian.

1283
01:30:55,967 --> 01:30:57,768
I mean,
Ngoc Lan, I will

1284
01:30:57,770 --> 01:31:00,466
be able to help
when I get back 100%,

1285
01:31:00,469 --> 01:31:02,335
and when you get
the new foot, and...

1286
01:31:02,337 --> 01:31:03,936
You leave Wednesday?

1287
01:31:04,335 --> 01:31:05,533
Yes.

1288
01:31:06,636 --> 01:31:08,502
And how long you go?

1289
01:31:11,636 --> 01:31:13,833
Ten days, maybe more.

1290
01:31:19,400 --> 01:31:21,801
Okay. Yes, Norway.

1291
01:31:21,802 --> 01:31:24,001
I go Norway, too.

1292
01:31:24,002 --> 01:31:26,265
No, no, no. Not you.

1293
01:31:26,268 --> 01:31:27,800
Only Paul.

1294
01:31:27,801 --> 01:31:30,734
I go Norway, too.
Paul, you help me on the trip.

1295
01:31:32,201 --> 01:31:33,399
But you're very busy here

1296
01:31:33,400 --> 01:31:36,365
with humanitarian activities
on your own.

1297
01:31:36,368 --> 01:31:38,497
