1303
01:31:49,233 --> 01:31:51,632
Feel so, so guilty!

1304
01:31:52,368 --> 01:31:54,500
They so nice people.

1305
01:31:55,199 --> 01:31:56,465
What?

1306
01:31:56,466 --> 01:31:58,132
Who invited you?

1307
01:31:59,565 --> 01:32:03,166
When I hospital so long time
after TV box,

1308
01:32:03,167 --> 01:32:05,363
people all over world

1309
01:32:05,365 --> 01:32:08,997
send me happy card,
flower, candy.

1310
01:32:08,998 --> 01:32:10,597
Make me feel good.

1311
01:32:11,131 --> 01:32:12,529
So many letter.

1312
01:32:12,532 --> 01:32:15,398
One letter very special
I never forget.

1313
01:32:15,399 --> 01:32:17,865
From Jorgen Asbjornsen.

1314
01:32:19,398 --> 01:32:21,963
You got a letter
